research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1648:research/history/logs/agent_action_0133.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。在线侧可导出为“共享低秩投影 + 单 expert 路由 + expert 内 local top-k + 静态子库查表加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r132 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `two_stage_residual_expert` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答当前高优先级问题“expert 内部 low-rank head / local top-k”是否比 trunk-free staged residual 更值得继续；如果该 family 在约 0.21x total_cost 下明显优于现有 `expert_topk` / `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的低成本负信号，则说明当前低成本带更有价值的不是继续打磨旧 shared+routed 结构，而是把低秩限制放进 expert 内部 head。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.21x 下显著优于现有同级低成本 anchor，则下一轮保持 `factorized_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试 expert-internal low-rank 是否还能进一步左移。","如果该点只与 `expert_topk` 持平或更差，则可更清楚地判定“expert-specific low-rank head”在当前 target 上也不成立，后续应转向别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 上做局部扫参。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=factorized_expert_topk`、`factorized_hidden_dim=256`、`active_experts=1` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.09x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.21x，明显低于 r132 的 0.47x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮相对 r132 是纯架构切换，目标是补上当前 prompt 明确优先的“shared/low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”结构信息，而不是继续在已连续无改进的 family 上细扫。"],"reference_round":132,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r132 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert` 已连续给出非支配失败，继续在这两条线上调内部旋钮的信息增量不高；切到 `factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和 prompt 对 expert-internal low-rank 的明确指向。主要风险是该 family 历史上有弱信号，但那是旧轮次弱先验；本轮在当前 target 上用 matched recipe 重验，结论会更干净。","summary":"Round 133 应优先切到新的结构假设，而不是继续打磨最近两条已连续失利的 family。建议以 r132 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`，在约 0.21x 的更低总成本下直接检验“expert 内部 low-rank head + local top-k”是否能形成新的低成本结构前沿。","touched_files":[]}
