research/history/logs/agent_action_0134.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"192"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 256 降到 192，在保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变时，shared low-rank basis 仍能覆盖主要全局结构，而更窄的 shared scorer 不会显著伤害 routed expert 质量，从而把总成本从约 0.37x 压到约 0.35x，并直接回答当前最优先的 hetero MoE 线是否能通过进一步低秩化进入新的低成本结构前沿。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 在约 0.35x 下仍接近 r129 的 FVU=0.1219，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试这条 hetero MoE 线能否贴近 0.32x 带。","如果该点明显退化，则说明 shared branch 的低秩压缩空间已接近饱和，后续不应继续在该 family 上细扫 hidden width，而应转向新的结构假设或别的未充分验证 family。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `factorized_hidden_dim=192` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 允许 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` param-only override。","本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.22x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.35x，低于 r129 的 0.37x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":129,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r129 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 做旧 family 局部扫参，而是沿当前最有结构信息价值的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做一次定向低秩压缩，直接回应 prompt 对“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”方向的优先级。主要风险是该 family 在 r129 已接近但未进入 frontier，192 可能仍被现有 0.32x-0.37x 点支配；但这是当前最清晰的一次单变量结构压缩对照。","summary":"Round 134 建议回到当前最值得补信息的 hetero MoE 线，而不是继续在最近连续失败的 family 上切新架构。以 r129 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，用一次 matched-cost 压缩直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 是否能通过更窄 shared scorer 形成新的低成本结构锚点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0131.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert。在线侧可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r130 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r130 在约 0.29x total_cost 下的失败是否主要来自“always-on shared low-rank branch + single routed expert”这一异构组合本身；如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r130 的 FVU=0.2266，则说明当前低成本瓶颈更偏向 shared+routed 结构耦合，而不是单-expert lowrank+expert 这条线整体失效。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下显著优于 r130，则下一轮保持 `lowrank_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=32/48`，定位这条 `lowrank + expert` 线的低成本 knee。","如果该点仍接近或劣于 r130，则可更干净地判定当前 <0.3x 带里单-expert `lowrank + expert` 也不成立，后续优先转向 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在这两条线做局部打磨。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk`、`active_experts=1`、`trunk_rank=40` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, TRUNK_RANK=40, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","直接构造行为已自检，不再退化成 `topk`：`SparseCoder(..., architecture='lowrank_expert_topk')` 返回 `LowRankExpertTopKSparseCoder`，且 encode 输出与 `topk` 不同。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.11x、deployment≈0.16x、total≈0.28x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":130,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r130 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是回到 `lowrank_expert_*` 做局部扫参，而是基于 r129-r130 已给出的 shared-lowrank+routed 负信号，切到另一条高优先级未充分验证结构 `lowrank + expert` 做一次 matched-cost 架构对照；信息增量高于继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。主要风险是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在当前 target 也可能继续给出负结果；但那会把“<0.3x 带里单-expert lowrank+expert 是否值得继续”这个问题回答得更清楚。","summary":"Round 131 不继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做第三个非支配失败后的局部 probe，而是做一次 matched-cost 结构切换。建议以 r130 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，在近同样的 <0.3x 总成本下直接比较“shared low-rank + routed expert”与“low-rank trunk + single expert”谁更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
