research/history/logs/agent_action_0138.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{l∈S_res(r1(x))} γ_l(x) c_l，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，r1(x)=x-Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i-Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}；U={u_i} 是静态 shared low-rank library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库，C={c_l} 是静态 residual library。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量 routed experts 选择 + 静态库查表加权和 + 选择性 residual 补偿”，不依赖动态生成字典，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：当前最有信息量但尚无最小原型的槽位，不是再扫现有 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 hidden/K 邻域，而是给这条 hetero MoE 线补上一段全局 residual cleanup。相对 r134 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual cleanup”能否在约 0.60x total_cost 的中低成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该新 family 在约 0.60x 下明显优于 r134 且接近当前中成本最优点，则下一轮优先修好该 architecture 的 override allowlist，然后只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，区分瓶颈是在 stage1 shared+routed 容量还是 residual cleanup 配额。","如果该点有正信号但成本偏重，则下一轮在接好 allowlist 后只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 之一，测试 hetero MoE + residual 能否继续左移。","如果该点明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 或只小幅优于 r134，则可较清晰判定 residual 增益不足以抵消 shared+routed 的额外复杂度，后续应把预算转回别的兼容结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地编译通过：`python -m py_compile sparsify/config.py sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual, K=128, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，按 r134 配方（`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`）本地估算 selection≈0.47x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.60x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","本轮实际运行时相对 r134 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`；没有新增 env key，也没有改执行层语义。"],"reference_round":134,"self_review":"满足运行时单变量原则：计划运行时相对 r134 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 的旧 family 局部扫参，而是补齐当前高优先级但尚未实现的“hetero MoE + residual cleanup”最小原型。代码改动严格限制在 `sparsify/`，并已按 `sae-architecture-integration` 完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class 和 exact architecture smoke。主要风险是 residual encoder 的 1024x1024 选择成本本身就接近 0.25x，可能让该 family 的总成本落在 0.60x 左右却仍拿不到足够 FVU 改善；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。","summary":"已在 `sparsify/` 落盘最小新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`：把当前最有希望的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 接上一段全局 sparse residual cleanup。建议本轮以 r134 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，先做一次干净的 matched architecture swap，直接判断“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual”是否值得继续。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0130.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是 shared low-rank projection，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库；在线链路仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍属直接兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，在保持 `K=128`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 不变时，shared 分支已覆盖全局主干，routed 分支可以收缩到单 expert 而不显著伤害 FVU，从而把 selection cost 从约 0.24x 压到约 0.16x、total_cost 从约 0.37x 压到约 0.29x，并直接回答这条“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”异构 MoE 线是否能形成新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 在约 0.29x 下仍接近 r129 的 FVU，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 或 `128`，继续压 shared scorer 成本。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明该 family 的瓶颈更像 routed capacity 而非 active path 过长；下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 做 matched-cost 对照，而不是回到旧 family。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `active_experts=1` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist；此前该 family 对 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` / `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` / `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的 param-only probe 会在训练前被判为 disallowed。","本地校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，同时仍拒绝不属于该 family 的 `TRUNK_RANK`。","exact smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward；成本自检为 selection≈0.16x、deploy≈0.12x、total≈0.29x。"],"reference_round":129,"self_review":"这轮先消除真实 blocker：r129 之后该新 family 虽已可训练，但 AutoResearch 没把它接到 expert/factorized override allowlist，导致后续单变量结构 probe 无法合法发起。真实落盘改动只在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`，不改 trainer/eval 语义；计划运行时相对 r129 仍只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。风险是单 expert 路由可能让 FVU 回退到被现有 0.30x-0.34x anchor 支配；但这正是当前低开销阶段最需要回答的结构问题。","summary":"已落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 override 接线，使这条新异构 MoE family 可以继续做合法的单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r129 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，用一次 matched-cost 低开销实验直接检验“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert local top-k”是否能把该 family 推进到新的 <0.3x Pareto 段。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0135.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r134 仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 192 进一步降到 128，在保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变时，shared low-rank basis 仍能承担主要全局结构，从而把总成本从约 0.35x 继续压到约 0.32x；如果 FVU 仍接近 r134 的 0.1248，则说明当前最有希望的低成本结构段就是这条 hetero MoE 线的进一步低秩压缩。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128` 在约 0.32x 下仍接近 r134，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`，继续测试这条 hetero MoE 线能否再向左推进。","如果该点明显退化，则说明 shared branch 的 low-rank 压缩已经接近极限，后续不应继续在该 family 上细扫 hidden width，而应切回新的结构假设。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `factorized_hidden_dim=128` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 允许 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` param-only override。","本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.20x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.32x，低于 r134 的 0.35x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":134,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r134 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。r134 已证明这条 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 线在 0.35x 仍保持接近 r129 的质量，继续把 shared scorer 从 192 压到 128 是当前信息增量最高、且仍符合“进一步稀疏化 + 进一步低秩化”指引的动作。主要风险是该点会被现有 0.30x-0.35x anchor 支配；但这正是本轮要确认的压缩边界。","summary":"Round 135 继续沿当前最有希望的 hetero MoE 线做一次更激进但仍清晰的单变量低秩压缩。以 r134 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 能否在约 0.32x 总成本下维持接近当前最强低成本结构点的质量。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0129.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 仍是不兼容 family，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r128 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r127-r128 的负信号是否主要来自“routed experts 也被一并 factorize”这一结构限制；如果是，则新 family 应在 fresh cost 约 selection=0.24x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.37x 的低成本带显著优于 0.2248，并决定这条 shared-lowrank + full-routed-head 结构是否值得继续扩展。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.37x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿，则下一轮保持新 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `K=112`，定位这条新线的 low-cost knee。","如果结果只小幅优于 r128 但仍明显差于现有 `<0.5x` frontier，则可初步判定问题不只在 routed factorization，本方向优先级应下调，后续转回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构。","如果训练前或 sanity 阶段出现新问题，先按新 family registration/forward 问题处理，不要把失败误判为结构质量结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","fresh cost 自检：selection_accesses=1015808、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=1540096，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.37，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":128,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：计划运行时相对 r128 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到旧 family 的局部扫参，而是落一个最小新原型，直接隔离“shared+routed 失败是否来自把 routed heads 也 factorize”这个高信息量结构问题。按 `sae-architecture-integration` 检查，whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 exact architecture smoke 都已完成；主要风险是 routed full heads 会把行为拉回接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而缺乏新的 Pareto 价值，但这本身也是清晰结论。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
